1.name: Local news
1.text:
Filitrios Newest News

CLOSED!!!

FILITRIOS TOY STORE CLOSED!
On the 253rd day of the year 2092, the Filitrios Toy Store was officially closed after several cases of missing children were resolved. The towns near the toy store have had several large vain shroud infestations before. There were several infested areas near the toy store which could easily have been rid by the Filitrios company. Unfortunately this has let to many so called 'Kidnapper Foxes' snatching children around the toys store and taking them back to their vain shroud hideouts to be killed. The toy store was therefor deemed unsafe and the company was sued for their neglect.

THE DANGERS OF KIDNAPPER FOXES.
Are you curious about the dangers and beauty of Kidnapper foxes and how to avoid them?
Head over to our website:
www.kidnappedmyfox.comp

DESHROUD BACK IN BUSINESS AFTER COLOSSAL BREAKOUT.

4.name: Radio4
4.text:
Hello everyone, you are listening to Across the Stars and I’d like to apologize for my absence in the past few days.

Times are tough.

It’s currently 2:23 pm and I’m sorry to announce that this will be my final broadcast.

My sources are dwindling and finding any good news has been like searching a needle in a haystack.
There’s just not much good out there anymore.
..It’s all terrible.

For those still out there. I’m telling you to leave.
Find the closest to you and go.
Go to the Domes.
There will be salvation on Demetrica.

I will be going too.

The Triton military has been growing in numbers and they’ll launch a system wide attack to conquer our side of the region.
And I don’t want anyone to experience the horrors of what that will bring.
So I’m telling you again, leave.
Run for the Domes.

We will be going dark.
This was Across the Stars.
Thank you.

I’ll see you there.
